  "prompt": "How do I check my last 3 charges in Vodafone?",
  "response": "To check your last three charges on Vodafone, you can follow these steps:\n\n1. **Via the My Vodafone App**:\n   - Open the My Vodafone app on your mobile device.\n   - Log in with your Vodafone account credentials.\n   - Navigate to the billing or usage section to view your recent charges.\n\n2. **Through Vodafone's Website**:\n   - Visit the official Vodafone website and log into your account.\n   - Go to the billing or usage section where you can see your recent charges.\n\n3. **USSD Code**:\n   - Depending on your country, you may be able to use a USSD code to check your balance and recent charges. Common codes include *100# or *121# (or check Vodafone's website for specific codes in your region).\n\n4. **Customer Service**:\n   - Call Vodafone customer service from your phone. They can provide you with details about your last charges.\n\n5. **SMS Service**:\n   - Some regions allow you to check your balance and recent transactions via SMS. Check Vodafone's official site for relevant keywords and numbers.\n\nIf you encounter difficulty, it's always a good idea to reach out to Vodafone customer service for assistance tailored to your specific account and location.",
